		<u>Why Reinventor‑1 Exists</u>
Space is no longer a distant frontier—it is a critical extension of modern digital infrastructure. Satellites now support communications, navigation, science, and global operations, yet the security models that protect systems on Earth have not always kept pace with the realities of orbit.
Reinventor‑1 was created to close that gap.
The platform enables real‑world experimentation with:

Secure satellite‑to‑ground communications
Protected telemetry, logging, and mission data flows
Cloud‑hosted data ingestion and transformation
Controlled access to mission insights through a public‑facing portal

