What Reinventor‑1 Does
Reinventor‑1 operates as an integrated system spanning orbit, ground stations, and cloud infrastructure. At a high level, it:

Transmits satellite telemetry and mission data through encrypted, zero‑trust communication paths
Ingests and validates data through a cloud‑hosted backend
Transforms raw data into structured, usable formats
Makes mission insights accessible through secure APIs and web experiences
Supports experimentation across cybersecurity, communications, and data architecture

